verbose_text: In the group pretreated with t-BHQ, the accumulation of Nrf2 in the nuclei was significantly increased compared with that in the IIR group (P = 0.0043) (XREF_FIG), while the accumulation of NF-kappaB in the nuclei and the levels of p-IkappaBalpha in the cytoplasm decreased significantly compared with those in the IIR group (P = 0.014 and 0.028, respectively) (XREF_FIG).
